{"id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0001", "text": "[Cybersecurity](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/veilig/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0001", "source_slug": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie", "source_title": "ICT sector and NIS2: take action on time", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie.html", "source_date": "2025-06-16", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 1, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0002", "text": "The ICT sector is central to the NIS2 guideline, which will come into effect from the third quarter. These European regulations oblige companies to get their cybersecurity in order. Nearly 100,000 ICT companies in the Netherlands, of which more than 93,500 ICT service providers, are affected by this. Yet many companies have not yet started preparations.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0002", "source_slug": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie", "source_title": "ICT sector and NIS2: take action on time", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie.html", "source_date": "2025-06-16", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0003", "text": "The ICT sector is growing rapidly according to Statistics Netherlands. Between 2011 and 2023 there was an average annual growth of 4.6 percent, with a peak of 9.8 percent in 2023. Companies involved in software development, network management and cybersecurity solutions are particularly on the rise. Of the almost 100,000 ICT companies, approximately 39,000 employ staff. More than 58 percent consist of self-employed people without employees (self-employed).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0003", "source_slug": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie", "source_title": "ICT sector and NIS2: take action on time", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie.html", "source_date": "2025-06-16", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0004", "text": "Because almost every ICT company plays a role in the digital chain, the chain responsibility from NIS2 also applies to them. Customers will increasingly demand proof that ICT suppliers work cyber securely. Without measures, companies risk losing orders.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0004", "source_slug": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie", "source_title": "ICT sector and NIS2: take action on time", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie.html", "source_date": "2025-06-16", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0005", "text": "The NIS2 guideline sets requirements for risk analyses, security measures and supplier management. This takes time to implement properly. Anyone who starts now will be ready on time and build trust with customers.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0005", "source_slug": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie", "source_title": "ICT sector and NIS2: take action on time", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie.html", "source_date": "2025-06-16", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0006", "text": "With the [NIS2 Quality Mark](https://samendigitaalveilig.nl/mkb-toesuppliers/) companies meet all requirements. Do you already have ISO? Then you are already well on your way and you only have to implement the measures that are not included in ISO27001, but are mandatory under NIS2. This way you can be sure that you don't miss anything.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0006", "source_slug": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie", "source_title": "ICT sector and NIS2: take action on time", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie.html", "source_date": "2025-06-16", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0007", "text": "This article was produced in collaboration with [Samen Digitaal Veilig](https://samendigitaalveilig.nl/).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0007", "source_slug": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie", "source_title": "ICT sector and NIS2: take action on time", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie.html", "source_date": "2025-06-16", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0008", "text": "About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0008", "source_slug": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie", "source_title": "ICT sector and NIS2: take action on time", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie.html", "source_date": "2025-06-16", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0009", "text": "- Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) and reduce your cyber risks.\n- View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars on our [Safe entrepreneurship page](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link).\n- [Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie__c4-paragraph__0009", "source_slug": "ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie", "source_title": "ICT sector and NIS2: take action on time", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/ict-sector-en-nis2-kom-op-tijd-in-actie.html", "source_date": "2025-06-16", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
